author: Nerd of the Rings
description:
Today, we take a compiled (and extended) look at the realms of Tolkien's dwarves!

00:00-19:30 Moria (Khazad-dûm)

32:08-41:30 Mount Gundabad
41:30-01:01:42 Blue Mountains
01:01:42-01:15:12 Erebor
